segments.text: morning it's 8 a.m and I'm getting ready for the daily morning walk. Copenhagen is so rainy and
gloomy today but I kind of love it. There's truly nothing like autumn in Copenhagen. When I got home
I made my breakie and then match up before I started working. I honestly just sat here for so
many hours scheduling campaigns and doing admin work before I decided to meet up with my boyfriend
for a little afternoon coffee. It got kind of late so we ordered takeout and that was basically my day.
